api_list.name: Get Currencies List
api_list.description: Get a list of all the Currencies available
api_list.code:
import requests

url = "https://cities-cost-of-living1.p.rapidapi.com/get_currencies_list"

headers = {
    "X-RapidAPI-Key": "SIGN-UP-FOR-KEY",
    "X-RapidAPI-Host": "cities-cost-of-living1.p.rapidapi.com"
}

response = requests.get(url, headers=headers)

print(response.json())

api_list.name: Get Cities Details by Coordinates
api_list.description: Get all the details about the cities that are inside the radius of the coordinates requested, in the currencies requested.

optional_parameters.name: distance_unit
optional_parameters.description:
Default value is ```kilometers```

Possible values are ```km | mi | kilometers | miles | m | meters | feet | ft | nautical | nm```
